and it makes sense that a systems analyst would throw this into the equation. I do not visit this forum often so might not see your reply if you post one, however, your post was so interesteing and I believe on the money that I wanted to contribute my thoughts to the matter.<br>Safe journeys and good looting,<br>Bakabaka Khagan - Necromancer of Paineel<br>Now a Rogue as well.</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
